{"tid":1960313,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［2020DSE自修］通識卷一+卷二Mock","createTime":"2020-04-06T05:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T06:14:21.000Z","uid":125535,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"69c11c3ae4661490f4c1dd892f1e58875405767b","tid":1960313,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:34:26.000Z","msg":"話說今年DSE又遲左開考<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相信今年既考生都會好迷惘，不過都多左時間再準備，所以今次就準備左通識科既Mock比自修既巴絲們，仲邀請左日校通識老師黎解卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望比大家作最後衝刺同埋重拾衝勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有少量名額，誠邀自修通識既巴絲參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n流程： 事先係網上send考卷比大家，大家做完之後再send比老師改，最後就會係網上同大家解卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成個流程都會係網上進行，唔需要擔心浪費口罩，同埋呢個Mock都係免費既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">卷一收卷時間：10/4/2020(五) 1:00PM<br />\n卷一解卷日期及時間：13/4/2020(一) 1430-1730<br />\n卷二收卷期限：14/4/2020(五) 1:00PM<br />\n卷二解卷日期及時間：17/4/2020(五) 1430-1730</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既巴絲可以係google form到留低聯絡方法，會再PM大家詳情,名額先到先得啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">*自修生優先，如果最後仲有位可以俾埋中六同學仔</span><br />\nGoogle form：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/svnMiFLS2VVtUsY59\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FsvnMiFLS2VVtUsY59&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=54fa9e34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/svnMiFLS2VVtUsY59</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申1:到時聯絡大家既時候可能要出一出示自修生既證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">利申2: 社福機構舉辦既, 已補貼</span></span>"},{"pid":"319776e38da11bb3416cf9374d336d9ae1f32575","tid":1960313,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T06:32:21.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeea473c01a3c7f7b7ebf35b91e72ee50276d831","tid":1960313,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T06:32:43.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27263832e8ae1c3eca17ce1cbe9a7e2828fe3970","tid":1960313,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703727ab12e12f21fb8b93871c1f4820263c6903","tid":1960313,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:25:48.000Z","msg":"向十連進發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e2af82713b71d90a04dd8baa93e0495d44498e","tid":1960313,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:19:34.000Z","msg":"六連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1a283e520502b53283daccdd16ef0ca8e470c5","tid":1960313,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:47:25.000Z","msg":"七<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5868b2789968b9a85975dd3b2794875d29a0837","tid":1960313,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:35:41.000Z","msg":"冇人回咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？我幫你"},{"pid":"b535650355cfa5ec84eea0d098a3e6d60c2b94a8","tid":19603